News.headline: Loan Announcement: Jake Howells
News.short_description: Midfielder Jake Howells has joined Ebbsfleet United on a one month loan
News.description:
The Daggers can also announce today that midfielder Jake Howells has signed on loan with National League South side Ebbsfleet United on a one month loan.

The midfielder joined the Daggers in January and has so far made three appearances since joining the club.

Follow us on our Social Media sites for updates on how Jake Howells is getting on at Ebbsfleet United.
